{"tid":420190,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣無求無慾","createTime":"2017-10-01T07:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T11:27:57.000Z","uid":106663,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bb70f8577d133aeef601125f371218675d90a525","tid":420190,"uid":106663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T07:54:56.000Z","msg":"開始對生活無哂要求無哂目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會話想要自己生活得好富有 就算窮都無所謂 只要夠日常生活就得<br />\n唔會有咩人生目標 理想乜乜柒柒 平凡過活就好<br />\n亦開始無咩情緒起伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開始唔會點嬲點唔開心 同時唔會點有開心嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開始對人點睇自己唔在意 完全係I don't give a fk咁嘅樣 好似對所有野都無哂興趣 不聞不問 連自己以前最&quot;沉迷&quot;嘅興趣都唔會再有動力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得自己宜家好有行屍走肉嘅Feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人同我一樣定只係我有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f16e60c6de554b90ee0a86a9e121043c4e401c","tid":420190,"uid":105344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T07:56:15.000Z","msg":"我諗我都好快係咁"},{"pid":"07441b975671c00311b9a16c1ff56558d52c6c78","tid":420190,"uid":106663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:00:06.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無同類"},{"pid":"68e866a58130a8ea6bbcd8a821a644668377e4b5","tid":420190,"uid":106663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗我都好快係咁</blockquote><br />\n千其唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48f59b9def5e